60
00:05:25,310 --> 00:05:26,190
Li?

61
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:32,200
I knew you were home.

62
00:05:33,270 --> 00:05:35,870
I bought some barbecue
for a late-night snack.

63
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:36,930
I'm not hungry.

64
00:05:37,890 --> 00:05:39,290
